description: Lexicographically earliest infinite sequence such that for all i, j >= 1, a(i) = a(j) => f(i) = f(j), where f(1) = 1, and for n > 1, f(n) = [A083345(n), A374132(n), A374133(n)], where A083345 is the numerator of the fully additive function with a(p) = 1/p, and A374132 and A374133 are the 2- and 3-adic valuations of A276085, which is fully additive with a(p) = p#/p.
